## Key Patterns

### API Response Envelope
The backend wraps all responses in `{ data, meta, message }`. Always unwrap:
```typescript
const response = await apiClient.get('/endpoint');
const items = response.data.data;  // Unwrap envelope
```

### Auth Guards
```typescript
@UseGuards({{AUTH_GUARD_NAME}})
@{{TENANT_DECORATOR}}()
```

### Tenant Isolation
Every database query MUST include tenant filtering:
```typescript
where: {
  {{TENANT_ID_FIELD}}: tenantId,
  deletedAt: null,  // Soft delete
}
```

