## File Naming Patterns

| Type | Pattern | Example |
|------|---------|---------|
| Page | `app/(group)/route/page.tsx` | `app/(dashboard)/orders/page.tsx` |
| Component | `PascalCase.tsx` | `OrderTable.tsx` |
| Hook | `use-kebab-case.ts` | `use-orders.ts` |
| Utility | `kebab-case.ts` | `format-date.ts` |
| API module | `kebab-case.module.ts` | `orders.module.ts` |
| API service | `kebab-case.service.ts` | `orders.service.ts` |
| API controller | `kebab-case.controller.ts` | `orders.controller.ts` |
| Test | `*.spec.ts` or `*.test.ts` | `orders.service.spec.ts` |
| Story | `*.stories.tsx` | `OrderTable.stories.tsx` |

