## Testing Patterns

```typescript
// Unit test structure
describe('FeatureName', () => {
  beforeEach(() => {
    // Setup mocks, reset state
  });

  it('should do the expected thing', () => {
    // Arrange -> Act -> Assert
  });
});

// Mock API calls
jest.mock('{{PATH_ALIAS}}/lib/api', () => ({
  apiClient: {
    get: jest.fn(),
    post: jest.fn(),
    put: jest.fn(),
    delete: jest.fn(),
  },
}));
