## Do NOT

- Modify files in the PROTECT LIST (see `CLAUDE.md`)
- Use hardcoded colors -- use design tokens from `{{GLOBALS_CSS_PATH}}`
- Skip `deletedAt: null` in queries (soft delete)
- Skip `{{TENANT_ID_FIELD}}` in queries (multi-tenant)
- Return raw API responses without unwrapping the envelope
- Use `any` type -- use proper TypeScript types
